name: Inside Travel – Special Collection (Skull Universe)
description: Inside Travel is a piece from the Special Collection collection (Skull Universe), it brings as its main element the skull, for me, it is a very special element, which brings several meanings, I try to represent it in different ways, each one of them a curiosity of the our current society, this piece in particular, portrays despair and lust, showing how toxic these aspects are for our experience.
